    "tactics": "Ogres throw javelins as enemies approach, then wade into melee with their greatclub, using their reach to strike before enemies can close. They focus on one target at a time, attempting to crush them with overwhelming strength.",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Greatclub [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 2 + Melee Combat 4), Reach: 10 ft (Large creature with long weapon)\n<ul>\n<li>Margin 1: 12 damage (Large size, two-handed weapon: 10 + 2 = 12)</li>\n<li>Margin 2: 18 damage (12 + 6 Str)</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Javelin [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 2 + Ranged Combat 1)\n<ul>\n<li>Range: 30/120 ft (Large creature, increased range)</li>\n<li>Short range: 1 success = 8 damage (Large size: 6 + 2), 2 successes = 10 damage (8 + 2 Dex)</li>\n<li>Medium range: 2 successes = 10 damage</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Powerful Build:</strong> Counts as Huge for carrying capacity, pushing, dragging, lifting</li>\n<li><strong>Thick Hide:</strong> Natural DR 2 (already included in stat block DR)</li>\n</ul>",
